items.text:
🎥** PAID CASTING CALL**

We are casting several roles for a series of short narrative pieces that highlight the stories of real families supported by our organization. These stories portray authenticity, warmth, and emotional depth.

**Location:** East Vancouver
**Audition Date:** October 20th

**Shooting Date:** October 23rd; must be available from 10-4 (you will not be needed the entire day)
**Compensation:** $200

**We are looking for actresses/actors to play: **

**Bruna**
* Female, late 20s to mid-40s
* Mother; caring and loving. Must convey determination, worry, and hope while navigating financial and emotional challenges for her children.

**Aisha**
* Female, early 30s to mid-40s
* Mother; warm, exhausted, and hopeful. Portrays a single parent managing multiple responsibilities with love and perseverance.

**Steven**
* Male, early 30s to mid-50s
* Father; provides care and guidance amid family hardship. Able to convey emotional strength and compassion.

**David**
* Male, mid-30s to 50s
* Father; supportive, patient, and empathetic. Represents the emotional toll of parenting through challenges while remaining steadfast for his family.

Please send a brief introduction and your headshot to **communications@ldsociety.ca. **We encourage applicants of all ethnicities and gender identities to apply.

Following auditions, we will confirm if you got the role and your timeslot via email on Tuesday, October 21st.

items.text:
Hi everyone! We’re filming a short home video–style flashback scene for our upcoming film Feel the Burn and are looking for a few performers to join us.

Roles:

 • Girl (ages 5–10) – Caucasian

 • Boy (ages 5–10) – Black / African Canadian

 • Mother (ages 30–40) – Caucasian, preferably blonde, to play the girl’s mom

The scene will be shot to resemble nostalgic camcorder footage, capturing a warm and natural family moment.

Details:

 • Shoot Duration: Approximately 2 hours

 • Compensation: $75 per actor

 • Location: Metro Vancouver 

If you or someone you know fits the description and is interested, please send a recent photo and your contact info to feeltheburnmovie@gmail.com.

We welcome submissions from both professional and first-time performers!

items.text:
**💌 CASTINGAUFRUF – Liebe kennt keine Grenzen!**

Du bist bis über beide Ohren verliebt, aber dein*e Partner*in lebt weit entfernt in einem anderen Land?
Ein Online-Flirt hat dein Herz erobert, doch euch fehlt das nötige Geld für das erste persönliche Treffen?
Oder ihr träumt sogar davon, gemeinsam eine Zukunft im Ausland aufzubauen?

**Dann suchen wir genau euch!**
* Verliebte Paare zwischen **25 und 69 Jahren**
* Ein*e Partner*in lebt in **Deutschland**, der*die andere **weltweit**

**🎥 Dreharbeiten:**
* **Gesamtdauer:** 6 Tage (davon 5 Tage im Ausland)
* **Zeitraum:** ab **sofort bis Ende Januar 2026**

💸 **Es gibt eine Aufwandsentschädigung und alle Reisekosten werden übernommen!**

**🎬 Wer sind wir?**

Wir sind **Madame Zheng Productions**, ein deutsches TV-Produktionsunternehmen.
Für ein neues TV-Format suchen wir Paare mit unterschiedlichen kulturellen und ethnischen Hintergründen.

Ob das **erste persönliche Treffen** oder ein **emotionales Wiedersehen** – wir begleiten euch mit einem Kamerateam auf eurem Weg zur großen Liebe. Egal ob nach Afrika, Südamerika, in den fernen Osten oder ans andere Ende der Welt – wir machen es möglich!

**✨ Jetzt bewerben!**

Ihr möchtet euch endlich in die Arme schließen und gemeinsam eure Geschichte erzählen?

Dann schreibt uns eine E-Mail an:
📧 **casting@madamezheng.de**

Wir freuen uns auf euch – und auf eine Reise voller Liebe! ❤️

MODEL NEEDED FOR SHOOT IN CHESTER 📍
 
We are looking for 1 model for a restaurant photoshoot in Chester on Wednesday 8th October. The photos and videos will be used on the restaurants’ website & social media to showcase the experience of the venue.

Please comment below if you are available and meet the criteria for the shoot:
 
📆 Date: Wednesday 8th October. 
⏰ Time: 12pm-4pm
 
Requirements:
 
-       Age: Between 21-30
-       Female
-       Wearing casual outfit. 
- some playful tiktoks will also be filmed, so you must be comfortable with playful /sassy content (e.g like this: https://www.instagram.com/reel/DI4rOAITfbP/?igsh=MXd6cXFyaWtqdDdpMg==
 
💸 Compensation:
-       We have the budget to offer each model £125 for the few hours. 
- Food & drinks will be provided. 
 
More in-depth briefing will be given to those selected.
 
Please comment below if you are available and meet the criteria for the shoot and we will be in touch via Facebook DMs.

1)           Andrzej Rybnicki vel Łukasz Chmielowiec (38) – dobrze zbudowany, silny i wysportowany. Brutalny przestępca, który kiedyś kierował grupą przestępczą, obecnie prowadzi przykładne życie u boku rodziny, prowadząc dobrze prosperującą firmę handlową. Lekko paranoidalny – cały czas boi się, że jego konkurenci z przeszłości go odnajdą i skrzywdzą jego rodzinę. 

 

Data: 05 listopada

Stawka: 450 zł netto

 

  

2)           Mateusz Grzesiak (19) – uczeń ostatniej klasy technikum. Zgodził się pomóc w napadzie, licząc, że sporo na tym zarobi. 

Data: 05 listopada

Stawka: 450 zł netto 

 

3)           Paweł Grzesiak (47) – mąż Iwony, schludnie ubrany, pracuje w korporacji. Przyjeżdża, aby być przy żonie podczas identyfikacji zwłok.

Data: 05 listopada

Stawka: 250 zł netto

4)           Policjant z drogówki (30) – ojciec 2 dzieci, próbuje reanimować Nikodema. 

Data: 04 listopada

Stawka: 250 zł netto

 

5)           Nikodem Wolski (19) –  „Młody i głupi”, zaplanował napad, zachciało mu się łatwej kasy. 

Data: 04 i 05 listopada

Stawka: 400 zł netto za całość

Chętnych Panów zapraszam do wysyłania zgłoszeń na adres: casting.outset@interia.pl

W tytule maila proszę o wpisanie nazwy postaci.

W treści maila proszę o zawarcie następujących informacji:

1.           Wiek/wzrost/waga

2.           Nr tel. Do kontaktu

3.           Krótki opis doświadczenia

4.           Linki do sowich materiałów video – demo/wizytówka/scenki castingowe

5.           Aktualne zdjęcie

6.           Informacje o posiadanym i czynnym prawie jazdy lub jego braku

Nie zwracamy kosztów dojazdu/noclegu

**Poszukiwani statyści i statystki do programu TV – Katowice!**

Do udziału w nagraniach programu telewizyjnego poszukujemy statystów i statystek w różnym wieku, z wysportowaną sylwetką.
Lokalizacja: Katowice
Data nagrania: 21 października do godz. 15:00

Osoby zainteresowane prosimy o zgłoszenie się w wiadomości prywatnej – koniecznie podaj numer telefonu.

items.text:
Film Title: Clouds Have Bridges Too

Production Company: Wishing Tree Creatives

Director: Wanphrang Diengdoh (award-winning filmmaker)

Featuring: Adil Hussain

Location: Private home in Hertford

Shoot Date: Late October/ November (TBC)

Duration: Approx. 1–2 hours

Role & Requirements

Baby of mixed heritage or person of colour

Ideally: light brown skin, dark hair, dark eyes

Age: 12–18 months

The baby will portray the child of an Indian father and a White British mother

Scene involves only shots of the baby sleeping in a cot/bassinet

No outdoor scenes, no demanding or stressful filming — just peaceful, indoor filming in a gentle, quiet home environment

What We Provide & Expect

Paid role for 1–2 hours

Parents/carers must be present at all times — and are warmly welcomed on set

Calm, safe set with full health & safety protocols — baby’s well-being is the top priority

We ensure breaks, a comfortable temperature, and minimal crew

If you have a baby basket or bassinet, let us know — it may be used for the scene

To Apply:

Please email enquiries@wishingtreecreatives.com with:

1️⃣ Baby’s name, age & heritage

2️⃣ A few recent photos (in natural light)

3️⃣ Your contact details & location

4️⃣ Whether you can bring a cot or bassinet

We’re creating something gentle and beautiful — your baby’s comfort and safety will always come first.

Wishing Tree Creatives

#CastingCall #ShortFilm #BabyCasting #UKFilm #ChildSafety #FilmCasting #WishingTreeCreatives

Dance&Arts is thrilled to be growing, and we're looking for passionate **teachers** to join our team right here in **Birmingham**! If you love inspiring young children (aged 4-16) through creative and performing arts, we want to hear from you!

 

We're seeking instructors for a variety of classes. Do you teach any of these styles?

 

✅ **Dance (all styles)**

✅ **Drama**

✅ **Musical Theatre**

✅ **Basic Gymnastics (mat-based only)**

✅ **Arts & Crafts**

 

**💰 Great Pay:** We offer **£30 per hour**.

***Crucially, please include the position you are applying for and the location in the subject line of your email (e.g., Dance Teacher - Birmingham).***

items.text:
UK/EU Actors seeking representation.

We are open to actors who do not have Spotlight (yet) and who are seeking representation in the UK/Europe. 

ANC is a brand new coop European agency. We are at the very early stages and still building our client list and relationships with casting and production. We are not yet on Spotlight which is why you don't need to be either.

If you are looking for your first agent feel free to email us.

- showreels
- professional headshots 
- filmmakers.eu and etalenta links (both are free to create)

Open to everyone above the age of 18+
Based in the UK or EU

- we do not charge any fees. 
- our commission is 10% from all work we secure.
- we are non-exclusive so, you free to look/have additional agents.

email: ancagency@hotmail.com

items.text:
EDIT: 10/20 HAS BEEN FULLY LOCKED IN, BUT WE'RE STILL IN NEED OF FOLKD FOR 10/15 AND 10/24!

CASTING CALL

A new independent production company, Tu Bruja Productions, is casting Wilmington, NC-based background talent/extras for our upcoming project, “The Return.” It’s a psychological/paranormal thriller centered on a haunted house. And we need a handful of extras for the following dates:

* **Overnight 10/15** - diners in a local Wilmington restaurant where we’ll need up to 10 people to include in the background with a variety of ages. Call time would be 11 pm, and we would be wrapped well before 5:30 am on the 16th. Can arrive wearing casual clothing, but no logos, no green clothing, and no small prints to avoid camera “buzz”
* **Morning of 10/20** - office workers in a downtown Wilmington co-working space for about 4 hours with a prospective call time of 9 am to 1 pm. Ages 20- 65 would be great. Will need to arrive in business casual attire. 
* **Morning of 10/24** - need 4 to five people, couples and friend groups ages 18 - 50 are preferred to film at Miller’s Pond Park from 9 am to 12 pm. Can arrive wearing casual clothing, but no logos, no green clothing, and no small prints to avoid camera “buzz.”

It is a paid opportunity with a rate of $75/day for a one-day shoot with craft services available on set as well as film credit. 

If you’re interested and local to Wilmington, please email vvicenty@tubrujaproductions.com with your resumé, headshot/selfie, and working contact number. Please don’t DM, as I can’t read FB message requests. Thanks in advance!

#paidopportunity #ISO #casting #wilmingtonnc #FilmCasting #horrormovie #psychologicalthriller

items.text:
Hi guys, hope you’re all well. I have a question that I wanted to put out there to the collective as I don’t seem to be having much luck resolving it on my own.

I’m currently involved in various Acting workshops and I’m trying to find some kind of course (ideally a night course) that I could run alongside my full-time job.

I really want to properly learn Acting theory but other than degrees and postgraduate courses I’m struggling to find anything. Any suggestions no matter how left field would be greatly appreciated.

Thanks guys!
Matt.
items.title: Acting Academy | Professional Acting Classes and Training

topComments.text: Have a look at www.actingacademy.org it's run by Mark Pegg it's based online with inperson workshops. You don't it at your own speed and it will give you an all round of what you need for acting in front of the camera and stage  you really need to know it all. No need to audition either from Shakespeare to knowing what works on camera.
I'd also be interested in something like this. I live in East Midlands xx

items.text:
TV 2 Dokumentar søger en mandlig statist i alderen 30-40 år som er ganske "almindelig" af udseende. Det er til visualiseringsoptagelser på torsdag d. 23. oktober kl. ca. 13 til 17 i Valby til en kommende dokumentar.

Optagelserne foregår på et kontor, og statisten skal spille en kontoransat. 

Jobbet er lønnet via honorar.

Passer du ind i ovenstående beskrivelse og er interesseret i jobbet, send da en mail til nyh.casting@tv2.dk med en kort beskrivelse af dig selv, evt. tidligere jobs og et par vellignende billeder.

Facebookbeskeder og -kommentarer besvares IKKE.

🎭 Studenterrevyen 2026 søger tekstforfattere! ✍️

Elsker du at skrive sjove, skarpe eller satiriske tekster, der får folk til at grine? Så er det nu, du kan få dine ord til at leve på scenen!

Vi leder efter tekster til sketches, monologer og sange — alt fra skæv hverdagshumor og bidende satire til absurde indfald og musikalske numre. Erfaring er ikke nødvendig, bare du har noget på hjerte og en god idé.

📩 Send dine tekster (eller idéer) til forfatter@studenterrevyen.dk
#Studenterrevyen #TekstforfattereSøges #Revy #Humor #Scenekunst

items.text:
Chaos reigns in America.
A President who campaigned on bringing certainty to the country (i.e., ending the war in Ukraine before inauguration; ending inflation on day 1; restoring the country’s image in the world; restoring free speech in the nation) has achieved none of these promises. Quite to the contrary.
But what if this chaos we’re experiencing is not a by-product of Donald Trump’s policies? What if chaos is his sole goal? The ultimate distraction from a plan to drive the country toward his consolidation of power; and away from the protections of a free society and a court system sworn to the rule of law.

Could I have imagined waking up one morning and finding a U.S. President has ordered troops to police streets across the country. The rationale keeps changing from protecting ICE agents that are tracking down immigrants “based on looking Latin or having brown skin,” to stopping the horrendous crime going on in cities which major independent research sources report is actually down 30-40%.
After six decades of a Republican party arguing for primacy of state action vs federal interference, there is deafening silence in the face autocratic rule.

Are these actions being taken to create the very chaos and revulsion from law abiding citizens you’d expect in a free society?   Nothing here is being done collaboratively with State Governors, local police forces.

Like my neighbors, I watched in shock as President Trump told top U.S. generals described anyone who opposes his policies as “the enemy from within.”  Trump field-tested his plan to send armed troops under the guise of policing U.S. citizens, because of the chaos he’s creating.
The violence and death of law enforcement officers on Jan 6 is now a blood stained footnote in history, but rioters convicted in a court of law have now been pardoned.
Trump asked the nation to give him “one party” majorities so he could implement his vision for the country has done nothing of what he promised. Tariffs are forcing a return of inflation and rising prices; job growth has slowed – and the power sought to improve the lives of average Americans has caused economic uncertainty and chaos.
After ten years of trying to destroy Obamacare, Republicans now would gut this vital health insurance program to deny 20-25 million Americans their health coverage.  President Trump and Republicans in Congress knew the cutting healthcare insurance would force a government shut down.

There is a plan afoot for what we’re experiencing. Our only hope is connecting the dots and restraining the long term damage being caused to our economy, our values and our standing in the world.

I want my grandchildren to grow up knowing I did not sit on the sidelines, in response to this existential threat.  "Neutrality helps the oppressor, never the victim. Silence encourages the tormentor, never the tormented." E Weisel.

**NOW CASTING:** Parents of kids aged 2-12 living in California for a *Brightlife Kids *digital Campaign! 

**Rate:** $500 

**Usage:** Inperp/worldwide 

Parents remember a simpler childhood with fewer screens and more freedom, but raising kids now means navigating new, complex challenges: the constant buzz of technology, the pressures of social media, and a rising cost of living. You’ll ask a question and our Brightlife Kid Coach will help parents navigate tough situations. 

**Role 1**: Toddler Parent (3-5yrs old) questions about how to help a toddler express anger. 

**Role 2**: Tween Parent (10-12yrs old) questions about social media use. 

**Role 3:** School aged parent (5-13yrs old) questions about separation anxiety 

Please submit a selftape (no more than 30 seconds) to *lsteinberg@attn.com* introducing yourself, your child(ren) age(s) and why you need help. 

If you are comfortable filming in kids room this is a WFH opportunity (please note in email). 

**Brightlife Kids is free personalized support for California families. Kids ages 0–12 get free, expert coaching for sleep issues, worry, social skills, and more.

We’re currently looking for one last character — the “gym/party guy” — someone who enjoys going out, has a social lifestyle, and also takes good care of himself.

The flat rate is $125 for approximately 3 hours of work. 

If you’re interested, please submit your headshot + video reel/UGC example. Has to be LA local as we are delivering the product ourselves. 

We’re aiming to complete filming this week.

items.text:
Casting Call: NEWSREADER

Looking to cast an actor (male or female) to play a newsreader for a corporate training video. 

- playing age 35-55
- Men and women of all ethnicities open to apply
- Natural US accent preferred but British RP also potentially an option
- Will need to supply your own wardrobe which must be an appropriate formal outfit for a tv newsreader

The film recreates a breaking news segment from an American news channel so we are seeking someone who can emulate the slick professional CNN newsanchor style of presenters like Anderson Cooper and Jake Tapper.

The job involves reading two short scripts from an autocue. Our filming time is limited so please only apply if you have some experience reading from autocue - this is not the job to have your first crack at trying it!

Fee: £125 for approx. 2 hours of shooting time on location in a central London office.

Shoot is likely to be Wednesday or Thursday this week (22nd/23rd October)

Please send headshots/spotlight profile along with any relevant work examples to me at Hello@jonfairey.co.uk and detail any experience in similar roles. No DMs here please.

topComments.text: Emailed. I work in TV news.

items.text:
🐛Casting Call 🐛
Super excited to announce our upcoming short film “Caterpillar” 

Please see the link for the application pack. 

We are looking for a Manchester based male actor with a playing age 17 - 23 to play one of the lead roles. 

This is a passion project so unfortunately this role is UNPAID. 

However this is an opportunity to work with an experienced up and coming team, with shorts already playing at BAFTA and BIFA qualifying festivals, to have footage for showreel and potential festival screenings. 

To apply please email the following to our producer India indiarainmedia@gmail.com, director Chey cheyennechristiecontent@gmail.com and Amy  amylever2000@gmail.com : 
 
1) A headshot
2) A brief summary of previous work and interest in the role. 
3)Your age 
4) A link to your spotlight profile / CV.
5)Your base 
6) Availability 

Deadline : October 27th 5pm

Please be aware this is a low budget short so we will be prioritising Manchester based talent.

We are hoping to film a proof of concept at the end of November with the provisional date of November 26th. We are hoping to shoot the short Spring 2026.

https://docs.google.com/document/d/1bliEA9aeNvZWR2WxKnnz6RPcf9G3D7QNAfFJtFq2Naw/edit?usp=drivesdk 

#casting #shortfilm #acting #actors #castingcall #castingcalluk #audition

We are seeking enthusiastic actresses for an upcoming independent zombie movie. This project blends horror, suspense, and dark humor. Shooting dates are TBD and will take place in the local area.

Who we are looking for? 

Women aged 16-28 who have a passion for horror! We have leading roles that need to be filled and want young up and coming talent to take that spotlight! 

WE ARE SEARCHING FOR TONS OF NEW TALENT AND ENCOURAGE ALL WOMAN OF ALL BACKGROUNDS TO APPLY. WE DEDICATE OUR PROCESS INTO INVOLVING AND UPLIFITING THOSE WHO MAY FACE BARRIERS. (If you need accommodations please let us know)

To be considered, please leave your contact info in the link below and our team will be in contact shortly.

I hope this is ok to post and please share with anyone who may benefit from this.

5 day free challenge Tame Your Inner Critic so that you can perform with more self-trust & freedom. Sign up to receive a link to daily challenge exercises.

 

Join my FREE 5-day ‘Tame Your Inner Critic’ challenge.

Stop the self-sabotage and start performing with self-trust.

 

That voice that picks apart your performance, tells you you're a fraud, and magnifies every tiny mistake? It's the biggest dream-killer for performers.

 

I'm Dr Maja Jankowska, a Clinical Psychologist specialising in the mental health of stage performers. I help artists silence their true biggest critic - the one inside their head.

 

This free challenge gives you the psychological tools to transform that harsh inner narrator from a saboteur into a manageable & helpful stagehand. We will learn the steps to trade pre-show panic and post-show post-mortem for focused confidence and self trust.

 

In 5 days, you will learn how to:

IDENTIFY your critic's unique triggers and tactics (give it a name and neutralise its power).

INTERRUPT its automatic, harsh commentary with a simple 'catch-and-reframe' technique.

CREATE a more balanced and compassionate inner dialogue.

PERFORM with more creative freedom and self-trust, because you're no longer your own worst enemy.

 

The challenge starts on 27th October.

 

The goal isn't to never have a critical thought again. It's to stop that thought from running the show.

Ready to trade self-sabotage for self-leadership?

 

Click the link below or scan a QR code to sign up.

[https://bit.ly/3KPB9z9](https://bit.ly/3KPB9z9)

Join me now! Linkinthebio Link in the bio Dr Maja Jankowska www.expansionpsychology.con'

items.text:
🚨ANGEPASST 🚨

🎬 **Schauspieler & Schauspielerin für Werbedreh gesucht (bezahlt, 750€ p.P.)**

Wir suchen **2 Darsteller (m/w, ca. 30–45 Jahre)** für **Social-Media-Werbeanzeigen im Immobilien-Bereich.**

📍 **Ort:** Hof (Bayern)
📅 **Datum:** Montag, **20.10.2025 (Start ca. 10-11 Uhr)**
⏱️ **Dauer:** ca. 5–6 Stunden
💶 **Gage:** 750 € pro Person 

**Gesucht wird:**
👨‍💼 Männlich – dynamisch, gepflegt, Business-Typ (z. B. Unternehmensberater, IT-Profi, Gründer)
👩‍💼 Weiblich – selbstbewusst, attraktiv, charismatisch, Karriere-orientiert
👉 Beide sollten den Eindruck vermitteln, erfolgreich im Berufsleben zu stehen und zur typischen deutschsprachigen Zielgruppe im Business-Kontext passen.

🎥 **Inhalt:** Social-Media-Werbeanzeigen (Business-Look, Teleprompter-Text, kurze Szenen)
👗 **Dresscode:** Business / Smart Casual

📩 **Ablauf:**
Bitte schreibt mir direkt **auf WhatsApp unter 01577 1082825**.
Wir benötigen **kein E-Casting**, sondern nur **ein kurzes Video**, in dem man sieht, **wie du vor der Kamera sprichst und dich präsentierst** (z. B. aus dem Alltag, Handyaufnahme – es geht um Ausstrahlung, nicht Perfektion).

👉 **Wichtig:**
Wir posten hier regelmäßig ähnliche Jobs – bitte schreibt mir **immer mit Ort & Datum** (z. B. *„Hof – 20.10“*), damit ich weiß, auf welchen Dreh ihr euch bewerbt.

CASTING CALL – TV SHOW: DON’T GET CATFISHED (SERIES 2)

The hit Channel 4.0 entertainment show is BACK and casting for Season 2!

LOCATION: London Studio

DATES: Thursday 13th or Friday 14th November 2025

PAID

We're looking for single men (28+) and single women (25+) who want their chance to bag a date with one of the UK’s top creators.

If you’re a Confident Queen, Rizz Royalty, It Girl, Zaddie, or a Reformed F-boy, and you serve main character energy, this show wants you in the mix.

THE TWIST:

Among the five mysterious blind "dates" (whose voices are disguised and identities hidden) are undercover friends of the creator, secretly trying to trick their way to a free date night. Can you tell who’s real?

HOW TO APPLY:

The hit Channel 4.0 entertainment show is BACK and casting for Season 2!

LOCATION: London Studio

DATES: Thursday 13th or Friday 14th November 2025

PAID

We're looking for single men (28+) and single women (25+) who want their chance to bag a date with one of the UK’s top creators.

If you’re a Confident Queen, Rizz Royalty, It Girl, Zaddie, or a Reformed F-boy, and you serve main character energy, this show wants you in the mix.

Hi everyone! My name is **Sarah Morgan**, and I’m a producer on the indie medieval fantasy comedy feature film ***The Kingdom of Rexmonte***. We’ll be filming in **Altamont, NY** from **October 20–25**, and we’re looking for enthusiastic volunteers to play **soldiers** in battle scenes!

 🍴 Full lunch & snacks provided
 🎭 Ren faire/medieval attire welcome
 🙌 Unpaid, but an epic film set experience!

👉 Sign up here: [[https://forms.gle/zqWmXjAw7sDqFRGv9](https://forms.gle/zqWmXjAw7sDqFRGv9)](https://forms.gle/zqWmXjAw7sDqFRGv9)

# (Paid) Casting for George Fox University Student Film, (Hillsboro, Oregon)

We are a group of George Fox students shooting a short film at the Airplane Home for our Location Production class, looking for a total of three non-union actors.

Project Title: Clearing The Air

Location: Airplane Home: 15270 SW Holly Hill Rd, Hillsboro, OR 97123

Safety Considerations: Dress for potential rain and cold weather. Several cats roam around the area, so be weary if you have any allergies. The actor that plays Jean will hold a non functional prop firearm.

 Shoot Dates: 10/28/2025 and 10/30/2025, 2:00PM - 9:00PM

Age Requirement: 18 and over

Pay: 50$ per day

You will receive a collection of your scenes to include in your reel.

Synopsis: Lost in the woods, siblings Gertie and Hudson come upon an airplane containing valuables. The sister aims to ransack the plane, while her brother urges her against it. Upon the return of the airplane’s resident, Jean, the sister attempts to escape with her spoils by attacking Jean from behind while her brother serves as a distraction. Her plan is thwarted by Jean, who catches her in the act, and Hudson, who reveals her presence and forces her to return what she stole. Once the two parties agree to part ways, it is revealed that Jean is a fugitive with a reward for her capture, worth more than anything the siblings could’ve stolen.

Character Breakdown

(Antagonist) Jean: A perceptive older woman with a soft face but a hardened demeanor, a criminal past, and a lifetime of secrets behind her eyes.

Age: The character is meant to be in her early sixties, but her age isn't a strict guideline.

(Protagonist) Hudson: A thoughtful late teen with dark hair, an anxious posture, and a subdued retro rock styling, who has a tendency to let others walk over him.

He is the younger brother to Gertie.

"Think William Miller in Almost Famous but more frazzled and sarcastic."

Age: Roughly 18-19

(Protagonist) Gertie: An outdoorsy, has-it-all-together college girl with a “Karen Carpenter” fashion sense, a hidden impulsive nature, and a proclivity toward not seeing beyond her own scope.

Age: Around 20-21 years old

Audition sides are in the link below. Please record your auditions and send them to Bronson Revilla at brevilla21@georgefox.edu.

[https://docs.google.com/document/d/1JdV5_ZnMYF6723lCAGBG3bluhEtj3u9prGwzw-Q1BcY/edit?usp=sharing](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1JdV5_ZnMYF6723lCAGBG3bluhEtj3u9prGwzw-Q1BcY/edit?usp=sharing)

items.text:
**CASTING CALL – Gaunt Man / Doctor (Dual Role) in Short Film *****The Damned Spot***

**Production Title:** *The Damned Spot*
**Company:** SWRCO Studios / Racetothefinishline Studios
**Location:** Atlanta, GA
**Union Status:** Non-Union
**Compensation:** $200 flat rate (2 half-days)
**Role: Gaunt Man / Doctor (Male, 40s–80s)**

**Character Description:**
This is a dual-performance role. The **Doctor** appears grounded, calm, and professional — a clinician trying to reassure his patient. The **Gaunt Man** is his nightmarish double: unsettling, skeletal in presence, and haunting. The shift between the two is central to the film’s psychological horror.

**Requirements:**
* Male, age range 40–85
* Ability to portray both a grounded, realistic character and a chilling, silent presence
* Strong facial expression and physical control — much of the horror relies on stillness and presence
* Comfortable with light makeup (pale complexion, under-eye work) and basic VFX markers
**Filming Commitment:**
* 2 Half-Days
* $200 flat rate
**To Apply:**

Please submit:
* Headshot and resume (or reel, if available)
* Brief note about prior experience in psychological drama or horror
* Contact information

Send submissions to: **studio@swrco.us**
**Deadline:** **10-24-2025**

The **Gaunt Man** is his nightmarish double: unsettling, skeletal in presence, and haunting. The shift between the two is central to the film’s psychological horror.

**Requirements:**
* Male, age range 40–85
* Ability to portray both a grounded, realistic character and a chilling, silent presence
* Strong facial expression and physical control — much of the horror relies on stillness and presence
* Comfortable with light makeup (pale complexion, under-eye work) and basic VFX markers
**Filming Commitment:**
* 2 Half-Days
* $200 flat rate
**To Apply:**

Please submit:
* Headshot and resume (or reel, if available)
* Brief note about prior experience in psychological drama or horror
* Contact information

Send submissions to: **studio@swrco.us**
**Deadline:** **10-24-2025**

🎬Osoby na plan filmowy poszukiwane🎬
💥Na plan filmu fabularnego „Vaterland” w reżyserii Pawła Pawlikowskiego poszukuję STANDINÓW - Kobiety i Mężczyzny, którzy będą zastępować aktorów podczas ustawiania światła i kamer do ujęć. 🍀Standin nie ma tekstu, nie gra aktorsko zatem może nim być każdy:) 
🗺️Miejsce nagrań: GOSZCZ (dolnośląskie,dojazd własny)
⏱️Data: 22.10 (dostępność od samego rana)
💶Stawka: 250zl za dzień zdjęciowy (wypłata blik lub przelew od razu po planie)
‼️Poszukujemy: 
💥- Kobiety w wieku ok 30-50lat, ciemne włosy, o przybliżonych wymiarach: 170cm wzrostu, klatka ok: 90cm, pas ok: 75cm, biodra ok 100-105cm 
💥- Mężczyzna Ok 40-60lat o zbliżonych wymiarach: wzrost ok 180cm, klatka ok 105-110cm, pas ok 95-100cm - rozmiar XL
📬📬📬
Zainteresowanych taka filmowa przygoda proszę o zgłoszenie na mail: WRC.STATYSCI@GMAIL.COM
W tytule: Goszcz 
W treści: imię i nazwisko, wiek, numer telefonu do kontaktu, wymiary (wzrost, nr buta, obwody klatka/pas/biodra) oraz aktualne zdjęcie twarzy i sylwetki 

Czekamy na Was! 
Justyna z Atlanta Int

Casting Call: The Chaos

We are seeking talented and passionate actors (18+) to join our exciting new Indie project! This is a unique opportunity to be part of a creative and collaborative production, utilizing **virtual production techniques** and **green screen technology**.

Requirements:

- Must be 18 years or older

- Comfortable performing in front of a green screen

- Enthusiastic about participating in an indie, creative-driven environment

Details:

- This is an unpaid project, but it offers a great chance to build your portfolio and gain experience in virtual production.

- Flexible scheduling for green screen scenes.

- A fantastic opportunity to work with a dedicated team on a passion project.

-IMDb Credit

If you're excited to bring unique characters to life in an innovative way, we'd love to hear from you!

To Apply:

Please submit a headshot, resume, and a brief video introduction.

They do not have to be professional!

We are looking for someone to portray these characters!

More information will be given after submission:

Chris presents himself as calm, confident, and even comforting. His tone is measured — he doesn’t command; he invites. He speaks like a leader or preacher, someone used to controlling a room through subtle persuasion rather than force. The steady eyes, careful pouring, and soft assurances suggest someone who knows how to perform sincerity.

Underneath the calm surface, there’s a manipulative intent.

Chris Myers (African American ages 20-30)

The theme is 'Miscast' so it will be songs paired with unlikely people. We ask that you fill out our audition form (found in the link below), send in a 2 minute self tape and the deadline to apply is the 9th of November.

**🎉 𝐈𝐓’𝐒 𝐓𝐇𝐈𝐒 𝐒𝐔𝐍𝐃𝐀𝐘! ** 

 

Get ready for the Actors and Filmmakers Networking Event happening on Sunday, 26th October! 

 

**📍 𝐋𝐨𝐜𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧:** HOME Mcr, 𝟐 𝐓𝐨𝐧𝐲 𝐖𝐢𝐥𝐬𝐨𝐧 𝐏𝐥, 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐌𝟏𝟓 𝟒𝐅𝐍 

**🕑 𝐓𝐢𝐦𝐞:** 𝟐:𝟎𝟎 𝐩.𝐦. - 𝟔:𝟑𝟎 𝐩.𝐦. 

 

This is not just another event; it’s your chance to connect with a dynamic community of actors, directors, producers, and writers who share your passion!
Networking is an essential part of our industry, so don’t let this opportunity pass you by.
Tickets are available at this link. 

[https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/actors-and-filmmakers-networking-event-tickets-1509159349239](https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/actors-and-filmmakers-networking-event-tickets-1509159349239)

 

Get ready to immerse yourself in a space filled with talented actors, visionary directors, influential producers, and skilled crew members, all eager to forge meaningful connections and who could help bring your next big project to life.

 

Also, if you're looking for captivating headshots or seeking to refresh your current images, the excellent Lisa Barton from Lisa Barton photography will be joining us at the event to showcase her incredible work!
Don’t miss out—make sure to stop by and connect with her!

 

Come and join us, we can’t wait to meet you 🌟

🎬 Hey zusammen!

Ich bin David, 55 Jahre alt aus Frankfurt am Main.
Ich bin 1,80 m groß, sportlich gebaut und vom Typ her eher südländisch & modern.

Ich habe zwar noch keine Filmerfahrung, aber richtig Lust, vor der Kamera zu stehen und in verschiedene Rollen zu schlüpfen – ob als Statist, Kleindarsteller oder für kleinere Szenen.

Ich bin zuverlässig, offen und bringe gute Laune mit 😊
Wenn jemand ein Casting in Frankfurt oder Umgebung anbietet oder Statisten sucht, freue ich mich sehr über eine Nachricht!

📧 Kontakt: teppichzentrum14@gmail.com

Liebe Grüße
Dieter

items.text:
🚨ANGEPASST 🚨

🎬 **Schauspieler & Schauspielerin für Werbedreh gesucht (bezahlt, 750€ p.P.)**

Wir suchen **2 Darsteller (m/w, ca. 30–45 Jahre)** für **Social-Media-Werbeanzeigen im Immobilien-Bereich.**

📍 **Ort:** Hof (Bayern)
📅 **Datum:** Montag, **20.10.2025 (Start ca. 10-11 Uhr)**
⏱️ **Dauer:** ca. 5–6 Stunden
💶 **Gage:** 750 € pro Person 

**Gesucht wird:**
👨‍💼 Männlich – dynamisch, gepflegt, Business-Typ (z. B. Unternehmensberater, IT-Profi, Gründer)
👩‍💼 Weiblich – selbstbewusst, attraktiv, charismatisch, Karriere-orientiert
👉 Beide sollten den Eindruck vermitteln, erfolgreich im Berufsleben zu stehen und zur typischen deutschsprachigen Zielgruppe im Business-Kontext passen.

🎥 **Inhalt:** Social-Media-Werbeanzeigen (Business-Look, Teleprompter-Text, kurze Szenen)
👗 **Dresscode:** Business / Smart Casual

📩 **Ablauf:**
Bitte schreibt mir direkt **auf WhatsApp unter 01577 1082825**.
Wir benötigen **kein E-Casting**, sondern nur **ein kurzes Video**, in dem man sieht, **wie du vor der Kamera sprichst und dich präsentierst** (z. B. aus dem Alltag, Handyaufnahme – es geht um Ausstrahlung, nicht Perfektion).

👉 **Wichtig:**
Wir posten hier regelmäßig ähnliche Jobs – bitte schreibt mir **immer mit Ort & Datum** (z. B. *„Hof – 20.10“*), damit ich weiß, auf welchen Dreh ihr euch bewerbt.

topComments.text: Habe auch per WhatsApp die Person kontaktiert

items.text:
Projekt: Kurzfilm „Zwischen Schatten und Licht“

Drehzeit: Januar 2026

Ort: Umkreis von 200 km von Nordhorn 

Format: Kurzfilm

Gesuchte Rollen:

1️⃣ Lucy

 • Spielalter: 26

 • Charakter: Nett, liebevoll, beste Freundin von Stella, loyal und immer unterstützend

 • Schauspielerfahrung von Vorteil aber kein Muss . Newcomer sind ebenso herzlich willkommen 

2️⃣ Nick

 • Spielalter: 25

 • Charakter: Gut aussehend, charismatisch, charmant, Sunnyboy

 • Natürliches, sympathisches Spiel erforderlich

⸻

3️⃣ Felix 

• Spielalter :20

Charakter: ehemaliger Drogemjunkie,Stellas jüngerer Bruder, Geldprobleme 

• Schauspielerfahrungen von Vorteil ,gefragtes Spiel erforderlich 

Story / Kurzbeschreibung:

„Zwischen Schatten und Licht“ erzählt die Geschichte von Stella, die unvermittelt in Gefahr gerät: Victor, dem ihr Bruder Geld aus einem Drogendeal schuldet, lauert ihr auf. Als Stella Nick, einen charismatischen jungen Mann, kennenlernt, funkt es zwischen den beiden — nach einem fast stattgefundenen Kuss stürmt Stella jedoch weg und gerät direkt in die Arme des Bösewichts Victor. Nick beobachtet die Situation und kommt gerade rechtzeitig, als ein heftiger Konflikt zwischen ihm und Victor eskaliert, der in einer Messerstecherei gipfelt. Eine spannende Geschichte über Gefahr, Anziehung und Vertrauen.

⸻

Bewerbung gerne per PN

 • Foto / Porträt

 • Alter / Spielalter

 • Kurzer Lebenslauf / Schauspielerfahrung

 • Showreel

items.text:
Mickey Mouse Horror Short Film
Hello, I am currently producing a Mickey Mouse Short film, with the working title, The Mouse Killer, which may become the actual title. 

This film is apart of my two existing films, My Horrible Roommate Winnie The Pooh 1 and 2. This serves as the next chapter within the series, that will lead into the 3rd and final My Horrible Roommate Winnie The Pooh film. 

Film Synopsis: two women are out in the woods, hunting down a mythical creature known as, Steamboat Willie, or Willie. 

If it all works out, this short film will be the start of a trilogy of short films. With the final one leading up to My Horrible Roommate Winnie The Pooh 3.

Actors Age Range: 21 to up.

Looking for two females who can play the roles.

Compensation: none

Location: Fort Collins Colorado 

If you're interested, send me a message!

Teatro da Terra acolhe 

O PRÍNCIPE DE SPANDAU de Hélder Mateus da Costa 

Sábado, 25 de Outubro às 21h30

Auditório Municipal do Fórum Cultural do Seixal 

com Gil Filipe 

encenação A BARRACA 

info e reservas    932 195 570    reservas.teatrodaterra@gmail.com

Bilheteira 

online em BOL.pt

Biblioteca Municipal e Bilheteira do Fórum Cultural do Seixal 

O *Príncipe de Spandau* é uma ficção provocatória e absurda sobre a vida de Rudolph Hess na sua cela em Spandau desde o julgamento de Nuremberga até à sua morte/suicídio.

Isolado na sua loucura, ele imagina que a sua prisão se transforma no Quartel-General de Spandau de onde ele, como representante de Hitler, dirige a política mundial enviando telegramas para ditadores, chefes militares e polícias de todo o mundo.

Ele é um príncipe encantado com visões apocalípticas sobre o regresso do Führer e a sua vitória definitiva. E quando vê o seu fim aproximar-se, vê a sua morte como o prenúncio de uma nova era em que o nazismo renascerá das cinzas.

O texto foi escrito em 1987 nos dias que se seguiram à morte de Rudolph Hess. Revelou-se premonitório em muitos aspectos e surge como um aviso contra as tendências racistas, ódios contra emigrantes e refugiados, despotismo e extremismos políticos hoje, infelizmente, mais vivos que nunca.

Citarei um excerto da peça sobre a ascensão de Hitler ao poder:� "Dizem que tudo esteve a nosso favor: a crise de 1929, as manobras dos magnates e da Bolsa, a corrupção dos governos. Esteve tanto a nosso favor, como a favor dos nossos inimigos. As mudanças no mundo não acontecem por milagre. As sociedades mudam porque há conflitos de interesse, porque há luta de classes.�E nós é que ganhámos essa luta de classes."

Só quero que esta História - mesmo em farsa - não se repita.

Hélder Mateus da Costa 

parceria

Município do Seixal 

apoio

República Portuguesa 

Direção-Geral das Artes

🎬 Short Film “ Glasses” (London)

Hi everyone,

I’m Anil an independent filmmaker currently working on a short film titled “Glasses” — a heartfelt story about an encounter between two strangers.

🎥 Shoot: 1–2 days in London (2nd or 3rd week of Nov 2025)

💰 Type: Independent short - paid, with credits, meals, and footage for reel - details will be shared and discussed once shortlisted.

Casting:

1️⃣ Male (25–35) – expressive, natural, grounded.

2️⃣ Male (60–70) – warm, witty, emotionally subtle.

If interested, please send a short self-tape / intro video and your availability to:

📧 angopproduction@gmail.com

I’m happy to share the script and concept note with shortlisted actors.

#CastingCall #ShortFilm #LondonFilm #ActorSearch #MyGlasses

📸 MODEL CASTING CALL – PAID OPPORTUNITY (£250 + travel & accommodation) - STARTUP LONGEVITY SUPPLEMENT BRAND

Location: Eastbourne (exact location TBC) Date: Shooting 8th November – models will need to arrive the evening before Time: 8:30 AM start, finish time TBC (likely late afternoon/early evening)

We’re looking for 2–3 models who are comfortable shooting both stills and video.

Model 1: • Female, mid/late 30s–mid 40s • Natural aging, healthy skin • Active lifestyle look

Model 2: • Male, mid 30s–mid/late 40s • Fit but not “bodybuilder” type – more functional fitness / outdoorsy vibe

💰 Payment: £250 + travel and overnight accommodation covered

📎 Usage & Deliverables: • Online and social media (brand channels, paid and organic) • Print usage TBC – brand retains rights to use across all channels

Mood board attached.

Please share recent photos and short clips (if available) when expressing interest.

Thanks!

Angela Boehm Casting is now casting talent for a TV Pilot "The Land"! 

We are thrilled to announce a TV Pilot coming to Cleveland. We are looking for EXTRAS, TRAINED DRIVERS, STAND INS , and DOUBLES. This shoot will be split from middle of the afternoon till the middle of the night. (Times to be determined) 
This project will be taking place in the Cleveland, OH area ! 

Please read carefully below for details! 
DETAILS: 
Project: TV Pilot "The Land" Filming 
Location: Cleveland, OH area (MUST BE LOCAL) 

Shoot Date(s): November 15th, 2025 - More dates coming in the new year 
Background Rate: $120/8hr 
Trained Drivers: $120/8hr + $150 bump 
Stand In: $128/8hr Double: $136/8hr 

Link to submit: http://bit.ly/3Lki3Bb

Kind regards, Angela Boehm Casting Team 

PLEASE NOTE: This is just a submission. If you are booked, we will reach out to YOU.
Playing For Keeps stage play. Another Sincere One Production. We shaking the pot over here.

Hello, Everyone I’m Vosiey Fvogueswier a inspiring entertainer and career consultant! I wanted to take the time to invite you to our entrepreneurship program with Road 2 Stardom Productions L.L.C, helping entertainers/entrepreneurs advance their careers in the entertainment industry, also helping grow their brand/label while advancing their knowledge and exposure in the industry. The entrepreneurship program provides marketing for brand creativity to establish financially support for career endeavors! The program also provides Great resources and support for career Advancement, with benefits like Paid travel expenses (35% - 90%) covered, Access to On Demand advancement and training courses,  Consistent employment/resource referrals weekly and Access to advisors/consultant to assist with Career development like (Website building, establishing a logo, bookkeeping, incorporating organization/proper Doc filing, business/financial planning and etc!
 
If you’re interested please click the link for  submission or email us at road2stardom.inc@gmail.com for more information!

items.text:
Hello everyone,

My name is Kayuran and I’m currently working on my first short mobile horror film. The script is in progress, and I’m looking for passionate people who would like to join me on this creative journey.

I’m specifically looking for:
🎬 A professional film editor
🎥 A camera operator (based in Durban/Chatsworth area)

The goal is to work together as a team and create something special. This project isn’t about making money — it’s about sharing stories and giving audiences an enjoyable and memorable film experience.

If you’re interested in being part of this project or know someone who might be, please feel free to reach out. Let’s build something amazing together!

From 
KM PICTURE

👋Hi Everyone! I'm Ash, a movement practitioner and professional stage and film Actress with a BFA and an MA in Acting, and over 7 years experience teaching/producing. 

🍂I have 5 SPOTS LEFT at my **Art of Letting Go** workshop THIS SATURDAY! This is a 3-hour acting + movement workshop that helps you release the tension you’ve been carrying- in your craft, your body, and your life.

👉You do not need to be an artist to participate. If you’ve been feeling stuck, disconnected, or just ready for a reset… this is for you! It will be fun and transformative, I promise :)

💚DM me or Scan the code below, to book!

items.text:
📣🎬 CASTING CALL - Short Period Drama 

We are casting for The Stuntman, a 3-minute period drama made as part of our final year at UWE Bristol. The film will be shot in Bristol in the week commencing 10th November 2025 (exact dates TBC). This is a student project, unpaid, but with expenses covered. The film is intended for university showcase and festival submission.

Story:
Set in 1920s Wiltshire, The Stuntman follows Ed Morris, a small-town silent cinema owner fighting to keep his theatre alive as the arrival of sound threatens to change film forever. With his fiancée Alice by his side, Ed stages one last ambitious stunt in the hope of saving his cinema - and their livelihood. A warm yet bittersweet drama about determination, passion and the march of technological change.

Roles:
Ed Morris (Lead, 28)
Charming, intelligent, and hardworking. Outwardly confident, but hiding a quiet desperation as he struggles to keep silent film alive. Needs strong screen presence and subtle emotional depth.

Alice Fardon (Lead, 22–23)
Ed’s fiancée. Feisty, loyal, and practical. She supports his dreams but occasionally shows frustration at his all-consuming determination.

Community Extras
Townsfolk gathering to watch Ed’s big stunt. A mix of ages. Families, workers and individuals. To capture the atmosphere of a 1920s local community.

Apply by: 1st November 2025
To Apply: Please send a headshot, CV (or Spotlight/Mandy link), and any showreel/self-tape to: Scarlet2.Gerry@live.uwe.ac.uk

Please include in email subject: THE STUNTMAN & NAME

CASTING CALL for student project shooting in Leeds as part of the Northern Film School

Get in touch to star in our new film. Send us a headshot/showreel and we'll get back to you ASAP 🎬💍

Donttellthegroomfilm@gmail.com ✉️📤

'Don't Tell the Groom' tells the story of a bride to be having second thoughts on the day of the wedding and turning to her best friend, the maid of honour, for advice. 

We're looking for 2 actresses that will display a bond of believable friendship. If you make it through auditions there'll be a round of chemistry reads to follow.

Pairs of actress friends are encouraged to email in and mention they'd like to be paired as a potential consideration for both roles. 

Looking forward to making this film. It's gonna be a good one 👰💒

This is an unpaid gig

CASTING CALL for student project shooting in Leeds as part of the Northern Film School

Get in touch to star in our new film. Send us a headshot/showreel and we'll get back to you ASAP 🎬💍

Donttellthegroomfilm@gmail.com ✉️📤

'Don't Tell the Groom' tells the story of a bride to be having second thoughts on the day of the wedding and turning to her best friend, the maid of honour, for advice. 

We're looking for 2 actresses that will display a bond of believable friendship. If you make it through auditions there'll be a round of chemistry reads to follow.

Pairs of actress friends are encouraged to email in and mention they'd like to be paired as a potential consideration for both roles. 

Looking forward to making this film. It's gonna be a good one 👰💒

This is an unpaid gig

items.text:
🎬 CASTING CALL - Holiday Commercial 🎄

Non-Union | Paid Roles | Denver Area

We're casting a heartwarming 1970s nostalgia-themed holiday commercial for a property management company.

SHOOT DATE: November 9, 2025
LOCATION: Denver Area, Colorado
SUBMISSION DEADLINE: Friday, October 24th

USAGE: Full buyout

ROLES AVAILABLE:

CHILD (Male, 7-10) - SPEAKING ROLE - $700/day
Lead role! Looking for a talented young actor who can deliver genuine Christmas morning excitement. Must submit reel showing previous work. This is a standout role perfect for your reel!

ADULT LANDLORD (Male, 45-55) - NON-SPEAKING - $350-400/day 

Plays grown-up version of Child. Warm, relatable, trustworthy presence. Reel or work samples required.

MOM (Female, 30-40) - NON-SPEAKING - $350-400/day
Supportive, amused mom in 1970s Christmas scene. Natural reactions, expressive warmth. Reel or work samples required.

DAD (Male, 30-40) - NON-SPEAKING - $350-400/day
Bemused but proud dad, possibly behind camera with VHS camcorder. Reel or work samples required.

SISTER (Female, 5-12) -  NON-SPEAKING - $350-400/day
Natural younger sibling for Christmas morning scene. Great opportunity for younger talent!

-Meals provided on set
-Professional production environment
-Copy of final commercial for your reel (after release)

LOCAL HIRE ONLY - No travel or lodging provided

TO SUBMIT:

Please email video reel showing your acting talent, plus a headshot to:

[CollectiveCp.Casting@gmail.com](mailto:CollectiveCp.Casting@gmail.com) 

EMAIL SUBMISSIONS ONLY please. 

Thank you for your interest!!

# **🎬 CASTING – aktor mężczyzna (azjatycki typ urody)**

**Ekipa Activity Area**, zdobywcy 2 miejsca **w konkursie 48 Hour Film Project Poland 2025**, dzięki czemu zakwalifikowani do prestiżowego konkursu **YesWeCannes**, poszukuje:

***👤 Aktor – mężczyzna***

*wiek: 25–50 lat*

***azjatycki typ urody***

*dobra znajomość języka polskiego*

*doświadczenie aktorskie mile widziane, ale nie jest wymagane*

🎥** Termin zdjęć:** 14–17 listopada 2025

📍 **Miejsce:** Warszawa

Projekt realizowany w ramach **konkursu YesWeCannes**, z **profesjonalną ekipą nagrodzoną w 48 Hour Film Project Poland.**

# 📩 Zgłoszenia prosimy wysyłać na e-mail:
# **casting.kamilaboichenko@gmail.com**

W treści zgłoszenia prosimy podać:

*1. Imię i nazwisko*

*2. Miejsce zamieszkania*

*3. Zdjęcia (portret i sylwetka)*

*4. Showreel i/lub portfolio*

*5. Wzrost oraz wymiary*

*6. Dane do kontaktu: nr. telefonu oraz email*

Czekam na zgłoszenia i serdecznie pozdrawiam,

**🎥 Kamila Boichenko**

**Reżyserka obsady**

Casting Several Non-union, non-speaking roles:
Grandfather 55-70 years old, all races, healthy body type
Grandson 6-9 years old, all races, healthy body type
Must be Canadian Citizen

Rate:
Adult $6,000 + 20% agency fee
Child $3,000 + 20% agency fee

Usage:
3-year worldwide usage for print and video (excluding broadcast) with 3-year exclusivity in the oncology market

items.text:
🎬PILNIE  POSZUKIWANY MĘŻCZYZNA DO SERIALU „NA SYGNALE” 🎬
📅 Termin zdjęć:
22 października 2025 od około 8.30 do okolo 11.30
13 listopada 2025  – kontynuacja nie znamy godzin 

📍 Miejsce: Warszawa – Falenica (Uwaga: brak zwrotu kosztów dojazdu – preferowani panowie z Warszawy lub okolic)

🔎 KOGO SZUKAMY:
Mężczyzna w wieku ok. 50–60 lat, ➡️ wzrost 170–173 cm ➡️ pas ok. 110 cm ➡️ klatka piersiowa ok. 118 cm ➡️ krótkie włosy ➡️ bez obcego akcentu (wymóg produkcji)
👉 Poszukiwany dubler aktora. 👉 Mile widziani panowie, którzy dawno nie występowali w serialu „Na sygnale”.
 👉 Wymagana pełna dyspozycyjność w dniu 13 listopada  – dokładna godzina zbiórki będzie podana później.

💰 STAWKA:
200 zł / dzień zdjęciowy Wypłata przelewem (na konto) po zakończeniu kontynuacji zdjęć. Umowa.

📩 ZGŁOSZENIA:
Na adres e-mail: statysci.nasygnale@gmail.com
📞 Do wybranych osób odezwiemy się w WTOREK 21.10.
W tytule maila prosimy wpisać: ➡️ NA SYGNALE – DUBLER – 22.10 / 13.11
W treści zgłoszenia prosimy podać:
Imię i nazwisko
Wiek
Wzrost
Obwód klatki piersiowej
Obwód pasa
Miejscowość zamieszkania
Numer telefonu
OBOWIĄZKOWO prosimy dołączyć aktualne zdjęcia (twarz i sylwetka). Tylko kompletne zgłoszenia zostaną przesłane do reżysera.
Wybrana osoba zostanie poinformowana SMS-em.

items.text:
Für meinen kommenden Kurzfilm „Zwischen Licht und Schatten“ (Drehort gebe ich noch bekannt) am 10.01 und 11.01 suche ich noch engagierte Mitwirkende:

🎬 Regie

Ich suche eine/n Regisseur:in, die/der Lust hat, gemeinsam mit mir diesen emotional intensiven Kurzfilm umzusetzen. Das Projekt ist charaktergetrieben und bewegt sich zwischen innerem Konflikt, familiärer Bindung und Selbstfindung.

Erfahrung ist wünschenswert, aber kein Muss — wichtiger ist Leidenschaft, Teamgeist und Gespür für authentisches Schauspiel.

🎭 Rollen

👩‍🦰 Lucy (ca. 25–28 Jahre)

– Stellas beste Freundin

– herzlich, empathisch, gute Zuhörerin

– ruhig, aber präsent, gibt Stella Halt

– Spielalter: ca. 26 Jahre

– Drehtage: [1–2]

– Keine Gage, aber Verpflegung + Material für Showreel

👦 Felix (Spielalter 20-22 Jahre)

– Stellas jüngerer Bruder

– ehemals drogenabhängig, heute sehr zurückhaltend, manchmal verschlossen

– steht im Zwiespalt zwischen Angst und Stärke

– hat Respekt vor Viktor (dem Bösewicht , drogendealer), aber kann sich im entscheidenden Moment behaupten

– Drehtage: 10.01-11.01

Kurzinhalt

Die 25-jährige Stella lebt zurückgezogen, misstrauisch gegenüber Männern und misstrauisch

gegenüber Gefühlen. Als sie im Park den sportlichen, offenen Nick kennenlernt, entsteht eine

leise Nähe – doch Stella blockt jeden Annäherungsversuch ab.

Während sie langsam Vertrauen zu Nick fasst, gerät ihr Bruder Felix in ernste Schwierigkeiten:

Er schuldet Victor, einem gefährlichen Drogendealer, 5.000 Euro. Victor bedroht Felix und sucht

schließlich auch Stella auf, um an sein Geld zu kommen.

Eines Abends eskaliert die Situation. Victor lauert Stella auf – und als Nick hinzukommt, versucht

er, sie zu schützen. Er hält ihm sein Portemonnaie mit 300 Euro hin, um Zeit zu gewinnen. Doch

Victor wird wütend: „Ich will mein Geld – oder einer von euch stirbt!“

Nick sagt zu Stella, sie solle laufen. Zitternd flieht sie und versteckt sich hinter einem Baum.

Dann kommt es zum Kampf zwischen Nick und Victor. In einem verzweifelten Moment wird

Victor im Bauch verletzt und bricht zusammen. Als Stille einkehrt, tritt Stella hervor, ruft „Nick!“,

läuft zu ihm, und beide fallen sich unter Tränen in die Arme. Ein Moment zwischen Dunkelheit

und Hoffnung – und vielleicht der Beginn einer echten Heilung.

Drehtort noch unbekannt Max im Umkreis von 200 km  von Nordhorn

🗓️ Drehzeitraum: Januar 2026

💬  – gern per PN oder E-Mail an [de.pascalis1990@web.de] kontaktieren

items.text:
**CASTING REMONTY**
Szukamy WYŁĄCZNIE wśród ZDOLNYCH AKTORÓW ZAWODOWYCH. Szukamy bohaterów, którzy są ciepli, nieidealni, ale dobrze wyglądający, budzący sympatie, zadbani, ale naturalni. Szukamy wśród aktorów teatralnych, filmowych, serialowych, mile widziane nowe twarze nieznane z reklam.

**👉KOBIETA i MĘŻCZYZNA ok.27-45 lat **
Zadbani, ale nie przestylizowani jak modele z wybiegu, sprawiający wrażenie sympatycznych, swojskich, niedystansujący. To muszą być bardzo dobrzy AKTORZY - wyłącznie zawodowi. Szukamy wśród aktorów teatralnych, filmowych, serialowych. Mile widziane zacięcie komediowe, ale nie jest ono wymogiem. 

**👉KOBIETA lub MĘŻCZYZNA ok.27-45 lat **
AKTORKA, ciepła, sympatyczna i godna zaufania o normalnej sylwetce. Opcjonalnie mężczyzna AKTOR w przedziale ok.27-45 lat, sympatyczny i uśmiechnięty, normalna sylwetka, nie łysy, dający wrażenie godnego zaufania.

**📅Daty:**

Recall 28.10.25 lub 29.10.25, 
przymiarki do potwierdzenia, 
ZDJĘCIA: 7.11.25
Warszawa 

📧***Po informacje prosimy się zgłaszać podając kod klienta na adres ***marketing@atvfilm.pl do środy 22.10 do godz. 17 (Z TYTUŁEM REMONTY)

***Zgłoszenie online: ***[https://galeriatwarzy.pl/casting/remonty/4786](https://galeriatwarzy.pl/casting/remonty/4786)

***Jeśli jeszcze nie współpracujesz z Nami kliknij w link poniżej***
📌 Rejestracja online (dla nowych użytkowników): [https://galeriatwarzy.pl/zgloszenie](https://galeriatwarzy.pl/zgloszenie)

# **🎬 CASTING – aktor mężczyzna (azjatycki typ urody)**

**Ekipa Activity Area**, zdobywcy 2 miejsca **w konkursie 48 Hour Film Project Poland 2025**, dzięki czemu zakwalifikowani do prestiżowego konkursu **YesWeCannes**, poszukuje:

***👤 Aktor – mężczyzna***

*wiek: 25–50 lat*

***azjatycki typ urody***

*dobra znajomość języka polskiego*

*doświadczenie aktorskie mile widziane, ale nie jest wymagane*

🎥** Termin zdjęć:** 14–17 listopada 2025

📍 **Miejsce:** Warszawa

Projekt realizowany w ramach **konkursu YesWeCannes**, z **profesjonalną ekipą nagrodzoną w 48 Hour Film Project Poland.**

# 📩 Zgłoszenia prosimy wysyłać na e-mail:
# **casting.kamilaboichenko@gmail.com**

W treści zgłoszenia prosimy podać:

*1. Imię i nazwisko*

*2. Miejsce zamieszkania*

*3. Zdjęcia (portret i sylwetka)*

*4. Showreel i/lub portfolio*

*5. Wzrost oraz wymiary*

*6. Dane do kontaktu: nr. telefonu oraz email*

Czekam na zgłoszenia i serdecznie pozdrawiam,

**🎥 Kamila Boichenko**

**Reżyserka obsady**

Wir suchen die Gesichter für unsere Haupt- und Nebenrollen! Du findest, du passt perfekt zu einer dieser Figuren? Dann melde dich bei uns! Ganz einfach via Mail deine Bewerbung an casting@datingoffline.de senden 📨

URGENT Cast & Crew call - Short film ‘All that we feared’ 

(posting on behalf of our director) 

We’re looking for dedicated actors and crew members to join our upcoming short film All That We Feared, filming in Hatfield, Hertfordshire on October 22nd, November 2nd and 3rd.

Roles Needed:
• 1 Main Male Actor (Arlo 17years old. All dates)
• Crew members (all departments welcome – sound, camera, lighting, etc.)

Unpaid with experience and credit provided. 

Location: Hatfield, Hertfordshire
Shoot Dates: 22nd October, 2nd and 3rd November
Apply now: Rdawsonproductions@outlook.com

Please include your name, the role you’re interested in, a showreel (if available).

items.text:
📸 2 STATISTER SØGES TIL FOTOOPTAGELSER I KOLDING

Pga sygdom mangler jeg 2 statister til en fotooptagelse på Comwell Kolding i morgen mandag den 20. oktober. Billederne skal bruges i markedsføringsøjemed for Comwell Hotels – primært til promovering af møder og konferencer.

Køn: Mænd og kvinder

Alder: 35 år og opefter

Hvornår: Mandag den 20. oktober 2025

Tid: Kl. 8.30–16.00

Sted: Comwell Kolding, Skovbrynet 1, 6000 Kolding

Din rolle: Mødedeltager og/eller forretningsrejsende

Dresscode: Casual business 

Forplejning: Morgenmad, frokost og eftermiddagsforplejning er inkluderet

Der vil være stylist og makeupartist til stede, som hjælper med et naturligt og professionelt look på dagen. Dog skal alle statister selv medbringe 2-3 sæt tøj jfr dresscode: Casual business.

Det er vigtigt, at du selv kan komme til og fra location, og at du selv står for transportomkostninger.

Honorar

Som tak for din medvirken modtager du et gavekort til Comwell Hotels på 1.500 kr. Bemærk, at værdien indberettes som B-indkomst til SKAT i henhold til gældende lovgivning.

Er du frisk?

så send hurtigst muligt en mail til LN@comwell.com med følgende:

• Fulde navn og kontaktoplysninger

• Alder

• Et eller flere nyere billeder i fuld profil (uden filter)

Billederne viser stemninger fra tidligere shoots og bruges kun som eksempel.

attachments.ocrText: No photo description available.

**CASTING CALL – BOULDER, CO**
**Shoot Date:** Saturday, October 26 (6 days away)
**Project:** *Under My Eyelids* – a heartfelt short film about an ex professional skateboarder reflecting on his memories of skateboarding after a severe TBI.

**ROLE:** Kid Cody (Boy, 9–11)
– Curious, brave, and a little shy.
– Comfortable standing or riding on a skateboard (no tricks required).
– Appears in an emotional flashback scene with his mom at a skatepark.

**LOCATION:** Boulder / Louisville area skatepark
**TIME:** Half-day shoot (3–5 hours)
**COMPENSATION:** Non-paid. Food, credit, and footage for reel will be provided.

**TO APPLY:**
Email **baxterdylan7@gmail.com** or call/text **(**970)406-2336 with:
– Child’s name and age
– Recent photo
– Parent/guardian contact information
– Any skateboard experience

This is a warm, character-driven scene about facing fear and finding courage.
— Dylan Lee Baxter
Writer / Director, *Under My Eyelids*

ACHTUNG ACHTUNG! 🐟 🌊 

Für das Projekt "FISHING FLIES" der Masterklasse Film & TV der FH St. Pölten suchen wir ab sofort nach drei Schauspieler*innen, die dem Film mit ihrer Präsenz ein wenig Leben einhauchen wollen😊 

**HARD FACTS:**
* Absurder Kurzfilm
* 6 Drehtage Anfang Jänner 2026
## **3 Schauspieler:innnen gesucht**
* Für ILSEBILL: Frau, 40 - 60 J. (ab 1,70m)
* Für MENNO: Mann, 20 - 30 J. (bis 1,70m)
* Für WILMUR BUTT: Mann, 40 - 60 J.

**DIE ROLLEN:**
* **Unsere erste Rolle ist "ILSEBILL".** 
Für unsere kampflustige Wissenschaftlerin suchen wir eine Frau im Alter von 40-60 Jahren und einer Größe ab 1,70m. 🧳🕹 

* **"MENNO" ist unsere nächste Rolle, die es zu **besetzen gilt! 
Für unseren impulsiven Agenten suchen wir nach einem Schauspieler im Alter von 20-30 Jahren und mit einer Größe bis 1,70m! 🕴🔎 

* **Und zu guter Letzt: "WILMUR BUTT"! **
Für unseren skurrilen "Fischbringer" suchen wir nach einem Schauspieler im Alter von 40-60 Jahren. 🐟💎 

Schreibt uns gerne direkt hier auf Facebook, an fishingflies.production@gmail.com oder meldet euch direkt bei unserem Casting-Team unter der Nummer +43 680 311 0685!  

Fish Out!🐟

If you’re interested, please email me at emily@aerialdragons.com with a reel or video showcasing your dancing (any style).

✨ Details:

 • Rehearsal: October 31st

Please email me directly for more information. We can’t wait to see your talent! Please submit by tonight or tomorrow morning, latest! 💕

items.text:
Dream Social – Remote (Contract)

Pay: $25/hour | Hours: 3–5 per week

About Dream Social

Dream Social helps creators who want to stream full-time grow, monetize, and build sustainable income through TikTok LIVE. We’re a fast-growing TikTok creator agency working with streamers all over the world , and we’re looking for a confident, camera-ready recruiter to join our team!

About the Role

As a TikTok Livestream Recruiter, you’ll host livestreams directly from the Dream Social company TikTok account, connecting with potential creators who are interested in joining our agency.

You’ll represent the brand on camera, explain how Dream Social helps streamers grow, answer live questions, and encourage viewers to apply.

This role is perfect for someone who loves TikTok LIVE, feels natural engaging with people on camera, and enjoys motivating others to take action.

What You’ll Do

    •    Go LIVE on the Dream Social TikTok account for 3–5 hours each week (in one-hour sessions)

    •    Engage with viewers in real time — answer questions, build excitement, and guide them through applying

    •    Represent the Dream Social brand with positivity and professionalism

    •    Follow provided scripts, content guidelines, and examples from other recruiters

    •    Track livestream engagement and report back feedback or common viewer questions

What We’re Looking For

    •    Confident and comfortable speaking on camera

    •    Familiar with TikTok LIVE and how it works

    •    Has hosted or streamed on TikTok LIVE at least once

    •    Energetic, clear communicator who can connect with an audience

    •    Reliable, consistent, and excited to be part of a creative, growing team

Schedule & Pay

    •    Pay: $25/hour (contractor role)

    •    Hours: 3–5 hours per week

    •    Schedule: Fixed livestream times that fit around your availability

Training Provided

You’ll receive full onboarding, training, and access to past livestreams from other recruiters so you can learn exactly what works.

How to Apply

Apply directly through Indeed with your resume. In the “Message to Employer” section, please also include:

    1.    Your TikTok handle

    2.    Your phone number

    3.    Where you’re based (city/state)

    4.    Your knowledge of TikTok LIVE (1–10)

    5.    Whether you know what a TikTok Creator Network does

    •    Follow provided scripts, content guidelines, and examples from other recruiters

    •    Track livestream engagement and report back feedback or common viewer questions

What We’re Looking For

    •    Confident and comfortable speaking on camera

    •    Familiar with TikTok LIVE and how it works

    •    Has hosted or streamed on TikTok LIVE at least once

    •    Energetic, clear communicator who can connect with an audience

    •    Reliable, consistent, and excited to be part of a creative, growing team

Schedule & Pay

    •    Pay: $25/hour (contractor role)

    •    Hours: 3–5 hours per week

    •    Schedule: Fixed livestream times that fit around your availability

Training Provided

You’ll receive full onboarding, training, and access to past livestreams from other recruiters so you can learn exactly what works.

How to Apply

Apply directly through Indeed with your resume. In the “Message to Employer” section, please also include:

    1.    Your TikTok handle

    2.    Your phone number

    3.    Where you’re based (city/state)

    4.    Your knowledge of TikTok LIVE (1–10)

    5.    Whether you know what a TikTok Creator Network does
